{
    "publish_date": "2013-08-30T18:32:55.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT14M51S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "I speak seven languages.", 
            "dur": "2.133", 
            "start": "4.75"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "As soon as people find out about that,", 
            "dur": "2.577", 
            "start": "6.883"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what I&#39;m most often asked --", 
            "dur": "2.261", 
            "start": "9.46"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "other than for my phone number --", 
            "dur": "1.972", 
            "start": "11.721"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is: &quot;How did you do it?", 
            "dur": "2.349", 
            "start": "13.693"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "How did you go about learning\nall these different languages?&quot;", 
            "dur": "4.353", 
            "start": "16.042"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, today I&#39;m going to\nshare with you some answers.", 
            "dur": "3.86", 
            "start": "20.395"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So my phone number is 212...", 
            "dur": "2.183", 
            "start": "24.255"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "1.113", 
            "start": "26.438"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m just kidding.", 
            "dur": "1.153", 
            "start": "27.551"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "See, I was raised as a polyglot.", 
            "dur": "2.039", 
            "start": "28.704"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And by the time I turned 18,", 
            "dur": "2.545", 
            "start": "30.743"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I could speak already\nfour different languages.", 
            "dur": "3.024", 
            "start": "33.288"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then for the subsequent three years,", 
            "dur": "2.351", 
            "start": "36.312"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I learned three additional languages.", 
            "dur": "2.005", 
            "start": "38.663"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s about those 3 years\nthat I want to talk about.", 
            "dur": "2.622", 
            "start": "40.668"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because my language acquisition process", 
            "dur": "2.804", 
            "start": "43.29"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "was very different from that of my peers,", 
            "dur": "2.664", 
            "start": "46.094"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in that it was never of these stressful,", 
            "dur": "2.477", 
            "start": "48.758"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "strenuous, difficult,\nseemingly impossible tasks,", 
            "dur": "3.607", 
            "start": "51.235"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but rather something\nenjoyable, fun, exciting.", 
            "dur": "3.437", 
            "start": "54.842"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I loved it, every single moment of it.", 
            "dur": "2.953", 
            "start": "58.279"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I want to share with you", 
            "dur": "2.445", 
            "start": "62.612"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "why, what was it that made it so special.", 
            "dur": "3.251", 
            "start": "65.057"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "See, I did have a head start,", 
            "dur": "2.476", 
            "start": "68.308"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in that I did have these four languages\nthat I spoke ahead of time.", 
            "dur": "4.056", 
            "start": "70.784"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But there were also these 5 techniques,", 
            "dur": "2.486", 
            "start": "74.84"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "5 skills if you will, that I use", 
            "dur": "3.243", 
            "start": "77.326"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that made the language\nlearning process so much easier.", 
            "dur": "3.282", 
            "start": "80.569"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it&#39;s about those 5 techniques", 
            "dur": "1.857", 
            "start": "83.851"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that I want to talk about.", 
            "dur": "2.045", 
            "start": "85.708"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So let&#39;s dig right in.", 
            "dur": "2.13", 
            "start": "87.753"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And for the first one,", 
            "dur": "1.409", 
            "start": "89.883"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the first thing that we&#39;ve got to do", 
            "dur": "2.195", 
            "start": "91.292"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is to take a very deep breath.", 
            "dur": "3.586", 
            "start": "93.487"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And relax.", 
            "dur": "1.89", 
            "start": "101.593"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the reason for it\nis because our entire lives,", 
            "dur": "2.924", 
            "start": "103.483"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we&#39;re taught how to do things right.", 
            "dur": "2.842", 
            "start": "106.407"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "From the moment we were born we&#39;re taught", 
            "dur": "2.121", 
            "start": "109.249"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what things we should do,\nthings we shouldn&#39;t do,", 
            "dur": "3.101", 
            "start": "111.37"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and how to do things properly.", 
            "dur": "2.671", 
            "start": "114.471"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, when it comes to language learning,", 
            "dur": "2.483", 
            "start": "117.142"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the golden rule of language learning,", 
            "dur": "2.208", 
            "start": "119.625"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the most important thing,", 
            "dur": "2.298", 
            "start": "121.833"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is to get things wrong,", 
            "dur": "2.956", 
            "start": "124.131"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to make mistakes,", 
            "dur": "2.086", 
            "start": "127.087"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and that is the first rule.", 
            "dur": "1.908", 
            "start": "129.173"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Let me explain to you why.", 
            "dur": "1.812", 
            "start": "131.081"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "See, when we&#39;ve known languages,", 
            "dur": "2.03", 
            "start": "132.893"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we know a whole collection of sounds", 
            "dur": "2.195", 
            "start": "134.923"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and a whole collection of structures,", 
            "dur": "2.667", 
            "start": "137.118"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which combined make what I like to call --", 
            "dur": "2.652", 
            "start": "139.785"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and for the purpose\nof this presentation --", 
            "dur": "2.15", 
            "start": "142.437"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "our &quot;&#39;language database.&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.238", 
            "start": "144.587"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And our language database will contain", 
            "dur": "2.054", 
            "start": "146.825"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "all the sounds and structures\nthat we know.", 
            "dur": "2.044", 
            "start": "148.879"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "However, there is a whole family\nof sounds and structures", 
            "dur": "2.726", 
            "start": "150.923"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that are beyond our database.", 
            "dur": "2.829", 
            "start": "153.649"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And for us to be able to embark on those\nand to be able to explore those,", 
            "dur": "5.424", 
            "start": "156.478"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "there is nothing within our database,", 
            "dur": "2.624", 
            "start": "161.902"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "nothing within our knowledge", 
            "dur": "1.803", 
            "start": "164.526"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that will tell us when\nwe&#39;re getting the structures right,", 
            "dur": "3.048", 
            "start": "166.329"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "nothing to tell us\nwhen that sound is precise.", 
            "dur": "3.575", 
            "start": "169.377"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Let&#39;s say we&#39;re going to explore\nthis one specific sound.", 
            "dur": "3.325", 
            "start": "172.952"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There is nothing in our database.", 
            "dur": "2.291", 
            "start": "176.277"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When we say it, we could say it perfectly,", 
            "dur": "2.749", 
            "start": "178.568"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but in our minds,\nit will sound like a mistake.", 
            "dur": "4.216", 
            "start": "181.317"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So you know that queasy feeling,\nthat insecure thing,", 
            "dur": "3.761", 
            "start": "185.533"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when we feel like we&#39;re doing\nsomething wrong?", 
            "dur": "3.76", 
            "start": "189.294"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That is the trigger\nthat you need to look for.", 
            "dur": "2.479", 
            "start": "193.054"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because that is the signal that tells you\nthat you&#39;re going beyond your database", 
            "dur": "5.54", 
            "start": "195.533"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and that you&#39;re allowing yourself\nto explore the realm of the new language.", 
            "dur": "3.982", 
            "start": "201.073"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Let me show you how\nthis works in practice.", 
            "dur": "2.065", 
            "start": "205.055"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Let&#39;s say, we&#39;re going to go\nand learn the word &quot;door&quot; in Spanish.", 
            "dur": "4.028", 
            "start": "207.12"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, the word &quot;door&quot;\nin Spanish is &quot;Puerta.&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.188", 
            "start": "211.148"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, for &quot;Puerta&quot; we&#39;ve got\na few sounds that exist in English.", 
            "dur": "3.19", 
            "start": "213.336"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, the &quot;Pu,&quot; &quot;e,&quot; and &quot;ta.&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.234", 
            "start": "216.526"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "However, when it comes to the &quot;r,&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.497", 
            "start": "218.76"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that sound is not in our database.", 
            "dur": "2.928", 
            "start": "222.257"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The &quot;RR.&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.31", 
            "start": "225.185"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The rolled &quot;r&quot; does not exist\nin the English sound database.", 
            "dur": "6.414", 
            "start": "226.495"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it&#39;s a little bit on the outside.", 
            "dur": "2.714", 
            "start": "232.909"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, if we allowed ourselves", 
            "dur": "2.67", 
            "start": "235.623"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to bridge through our database,\nand to really break through", 
            "dur": "2.97", 
            "start": "238.293"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and to make the mistake,", 
            "dur": "1.49", 
            "start": "241.263"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we could make sounds like the &quot;RR.&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.135", 
            "start": "242.753"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But instead, what sometimes happens", 
            "dur": "1.719", 
            "start": "244.888"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is that we get the closest relative of it\nthat is within the database,", 
            "dur": "3.803", 
            "start": "246.607"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and that is the &quot;ah-er&quot; sound.", 
            "dur": "2.377", 
            "start": "250.41"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "1.417", 
            "start": "252.787"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that &quot;ah-er&quot; sound", 
            "dur": "1.986", 
            "start": "254.204"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "makes something\nthat sounds like &quot;pue-er-rta,&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.618", 
            "start": "256.19"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which doesn&#39;t mean a thing in Spanish,", 
            "dur": "3.668", 
            "start": "258.808"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and actually doesn&#39;t sound too charming.", 
            "dur": "3.681", 
            "start": "262.476"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it doesn&#39;t tell you too much.", 
            "dur": "2.623", 
            "start": "266.157"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, for the first technique,", 
            "dur": "1.955", 
            "start": "268.78"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "allow yourself to make that mistake,", 
            "dur": "2.729", 
            "start": "270.735"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so that sounds like &quot;Puerta&quot; can come out.", 
            "dur": "3.29", 
            "start": "273.464"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And now let&#39;s go to the second one.", 
            "dur": "1.764", 
            "start": "276.754"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "For the second one,", 
            "dur": "1.311", 
            "start": "278.518"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m going to need\nsome of your collaboration.", 
            "dur": "2.096", 
            "start": "279.829"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We&#39;re going to read\nthese four beautiful words.", 
            "dur": "3.358", 
            "start": "281.925"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And on the count of three.", 
            "dur": "1.539", 
            "start": "285.283"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So let&#39;s start with the first one,\non the count of three: one, two, three.", 
            "dur": "3.667", 
            "start": "286.822"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Audience) Mao.\n(Sid) &quot;Mao,&quot; perfect.", 
            "dur": "1.746", 
            "start": "290.489"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The second one: one, two, three.\n(Audience:) Coco.", 
            "dur": "2.373", 
            "start": "292.235"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Sid) Perfect. Third one.\nOne, two, three.", 
            "dur": "2.127", 
            "start": "294.608"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Audience) Cocao.\n(Sid) Perfect.", 
            "dur": "2.198", 
            "start": "296.735"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the fourth one. One, two, three.", 
            "dur": "2.632", 
            "start": "298.933"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Silence)", 
            "dur": "1.768", 
            "start": "301.565"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Oh.", 
            "dur": "2.947", 
            "start": "303.333"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Let me show you what happened\nwhen we did this.", 
            "dur": "2.707", 
            "start": "306.28"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We get theses four words", 
            "dur": "2.309", 
            "start": "308.987"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and we put them through\na sort of American English filter.", 
            "dur": "3.676", 
            "start": "311.296"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And we get something\nlooks kind of like this.", 
            "dur": "4.764", 
            "start": "314.972"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I&#39;ll tell you the results of that.", 
            "dur": "2.05", 
            "start": "319.736"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So for the first one &quot;M\u00e3o,&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.333", 
            "start": "321.786"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which means &quot;hand&quot; in Portuguese,", 
            "dur": "2.172", 
            "start": "324.119"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we put it through the filter,\nwe get &quot;Mao.&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.796", 
            "start": "326.291"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "1.616", 
            "start": "329.087"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "For the second one we get &quot;coco,&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.108", 
            "start": "330.703"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which is &quot;coconut&quot; in Portuguese,", 
            "dur": "2.169", 
            "start": "332.811"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or &quot;coc\u00f4,&quot; which means &quot;poop.&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.346", 
            "start": "334.98"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We put through the filter,\nwe get a warm cup of cocoa.", 
            "dur": "2.748", 
            "start": "338.326"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "1.448", 
            "start": "341.074"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And for the fourth one,", 
            "dur": "1.999", 
            "start": "342.522"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we have &quot;huo,&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.344", 
            "start": "344.521"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which means &quot;fire&quot; in Chinese.", 
            "dur": "2.554", 
            "start": "345.865"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And we get --", 
            "dur": "1.154", 
            "start": "348.419"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "if you&#39;re feeling really creative,\nmaybe a dude doing karate...", 
            "dur": "3.036", 
            "start": "349.573"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "1.046", 
            "start": "352.634"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But anyway,", 
            "dur": "1.87", 
            "start": "353.712"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "these don&#39;t tell you much\nabout how these things are pronounced.", 
            "dur": "4.19", 
            "start": "355.582"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And if you think it&#39;s only one way,", 
            "dur": "1.916", 
            "start": "359.772"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "only if you&#39;re going from English\nto a different language,", 
            "dur": "2.794", 
            "start": "361.688"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "think about non-native speakers.", 
            "dur": "1.725", 
            "start": "364.482"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And try to explain to someone", 
            "dur": "1.616", 
            "start": "366.207"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that this [though] is pronounced &quot;though,&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.039", 
            "start": "367.823"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and that this [thought]\nis pronounced &quot;thought.&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.424", 
            "start": "369.862"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And even though\nthey look almost identical,", 
            "dur": "2.316", 
            "start": "372.286"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they have nothing to do with one another.", 
            "dur": "2.395", 
            "start": "374.602"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Or try to explain to them that", 
            "dur": "1.623", 
            "start": "376.997"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "this [enough] is &quot;enough&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.46", 
            "start": "378.62"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and this [enuf] is just simply wrong.", 
            "dur": "2.409", 
            "start": "380.08"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "See, there is nothing useful\nabout using that foreign alphabet,", 
            "dur": "6.618", 
            "start": "382.489"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when you&#39;re trying to learn a language.", 
            "dur": "1.991", 
            "start": "389.107"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Why? Because it will\ngive you wrong signals.", 
            "dur": "2.988", 
            "start": "391.098"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So what is the second technique?", 
            "dur": "2.391", 
            "start": "394.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Scrap it.", 
            "dur": "1.403", 
            "start": "396.477"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Scrap the foreign alphabet.", 
            "dur": "3.009", 
            "start": "397.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Let me give you an alternative\nof how you can go about this.", 
            "dur": "3.97", 
            "start": "400.889"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is a Brazilian currency,", 
            "dur": "2.041", 
            "start": "404.859"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and it spelled like this.", 
            "dur": "1.641", 
            "start": "406.9"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "On the count of three, can we all say\nthe name of the currency. 1, 2, 3.", 
            "dur": "3.398", 
            "start": "408.541"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Audience) Real.", 
            "dur": "1.435", 
            "start": "411.939"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Sid) We have some people\nwho know the spelling.", 
            "dur": "2.623", 
            "start": "413.374"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Yeah, &quot;re-al,&quot; for the most part.", 
            "dur": "2.43", 
            "start": "416.057"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And as useful as this might seem,\nit doesn&#39;t tell you a single thing.", 
            "dur": "5.486", 
            "start": "418.487"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And when you&#39;re speaking Portuguese,\n&quot;re-al&quot; means nothing.", 
            "dur": "3.472", 
            "start": "423.973"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Let me give you an alternative.", 
            "dur": "1.499", 
            "start": "427.445"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "See, in Portuguese,\nthe way that you say &quot;real&quot; is &quot;heou.&quot;", 
            "dur": "4.699", 
            "start": "428.944"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So let me teach you how to say it.", 
            "dur": "3.074", 
            "start": "433.652"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So on the count of three, let&#39;s say &quot;he.&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.286", 
            "start": "436.726"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So it&#39;s &quot;hey&quot; without the &quot;y&quot; sound.", 
            "dur": "2.169", 
            "start": "439.012"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, one, two, three -- &quot;he.&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.131", 
            "start": "441.181"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Audience) HE.\n(Sid) Perfect.", 
            "dur": "1.711", 
            "start": "443.312"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And now let&#39;s say &quot;ou.&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.433", 
            "start": "445.023"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s like &quot;ouch&quot;,\nbut without the &quot;ch&quot; sound,", 
            "dur": "2.416", 
            "start": "446.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so it&#39;s &quot;ou.&quot; One, two, three,", 
            "dur": "2.126", 
            "start": "448.872"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Audience) OU.\n(Sid) Perfect.", 
            "dur": "1.802", 
            "start": "451.008"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, &quot;HE.&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.074", 
            "start": "452.81"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Audience) HE.", 
            "dur": "1.299", 
            "start": "453.884"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Sid) &quot;OU.&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.337", 
            "start": "455.183"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Audience:) OU.", 
            "dur": "1.06", 
            "start": "456.52"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Sid) &quot;HE.&quot;\n(Audience:) HE.", 
            "dur": "1.31", 
            "start": "457.58"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Sid) &quot;OU.&quot;\n(Audience:) OU.", 
            "dur": "1.418", 
            "start": "458.89"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Sid) &quot;HE-OU,&quot; HEOU.", 
            "dur": "3.664", 
            "start": "460.308"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Audience) HE-OU.\n(Sid) Perfect.", 
            "dur": "2.758", 
            "start": "463.972"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now you all sound like\npassionate Brazilian capitalists.", 
            "dur": "3.184", 
            "start": "466.73"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "1.684", 
            "start": "469.914"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So why would we go and use\nsomething that looks like this,", 
            "dur": "6.604", 
            "start": "471.598"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that looks like &quot;real,&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.001", 
            "start": "478.202"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when instead you can use something", 
            "dur": "1.832", 
            "start": "480.203"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that looks like this and gives you\nso much more information", 
            "dur": "3.117", 
            "start": "482.035"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "about how to say something\nin a foreign language.", 
            "dur": "3.642", 
            "start": "485.152"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that puts us in a really good spot", 
            "dur": "1.814", 
            "start": "488.794"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because at this point we allowed ourselves", 
            "dur": "2.319", 
            "start": "490.608"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to break through our database\nand to make mistakes,", 
            "dur": "2.884", 
            "start": "492.927"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to go into that uncharted territory\nof a new language.", 
            "dur": "3.667", 
            "start": "495.811"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then, we figured out\nhow to take notations", 
            "dur": "3.179", 
            "start": "499.478"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in a way that the information\nis actually meaningful.", 
            "dur": "3.135", 
            "start": "502.657"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But then how can we test it?", 
            "dur": "2.259", 
            "start": "505.792"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that&#39;s where\ntechnique number 3 comes in.", 
            "dur": "2.955", 
            "start": "508.051"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Technique number 3\nis about finding a stickler.", 
            "dur": "4.005", 
            "start": "511.006"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So finding someone who&#39;s detail-oriented", 
            "dur": "2.798", 
            "start": "515.011"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and won&#39;t let you to get away\nwith the mistakes.", 
            "dur": "2.711", 
            "start": "517.809"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And more than finding someone\nwho is really that person,", 
            "dur": "3.345", 
            "start": "520.52"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the guru for the language,", 
            "dur": "1.8", 
            "start": "523.865"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s more about establishing\nthe right sort of relationship.", 
            "dur": "4.037", 
            "start": "525.665"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Relationship with someone,", 
            "dur": "1.386", 
            "start": "529.702"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "where they&#39;ll correct you,\nand feel comfortable correcting you", 
            "dur": "2.928", 
            "start": "531.088"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and making sure that you&#39;re getting\nto that spot you wanted in a language.", 
            "dur": "3.853", 
            "start": "534.016"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But at the same time,", 
            "dur": "1.565", 
            "start": "537.869"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "someone who will encourage you", 
            "dur": "1.445", 
            "start": "539.434"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to get things wrong and to make\nthose mistakes in the first place.", 
            "dur": "3.267", 
            "start": "540.879"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And sticklers could be your teacher,", 
            "dur": "2.593", 
            "start": "544.146"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it could be your tutor, friend,", 
            "dur": "1.743", 
            "start": "546.739"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it could be someone on Skype\nor on Craigslist; it doesn&#39;t matter.", 
            "dur": "4.104", 
            "start": "548.482"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You can find sticklers all over the place,", 
            "dur": "2.009", 
            "start": "552.586"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and with technology,\nit becomes a lot easier find them.", 
            "dur": "3.189", 
            "start": "554.595"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then it&#39;s time to practice.", 
            "dur": "3.261", 
            "start": "557.784"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And for practicing,\nwe&#39;ve got the fourth technique.", 
            "dur": "3.441", 
            "start": "561.045"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "See, I always thought I had this thing", 
            "dur": "1.936", 
            "start": "564.486"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that was a little bit\nof &quot;Sid craziness&quot; that I did,", 
            "dur": "3.958", 
            "start": "566.454"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and then I realized how useful it was.", 
            "dur": "2.259", 
            "start": "570.412"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I always did what I like to call\n&quot;Shower Conversations.&quot;", 
            "dur": "6.064", 
            "start": "572.671"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And shower conversations are\nexactly what they sound like.", 
            "dur": "3.767", 
            "start": "578.735"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When I was learning a new language,", 
            "dur": "1.751", 
            "start": "582.502"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I would stay in the shower\nfor a few minutes.", 
            "dur": "2.281", 
            "start": "584.253"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I would remember\nhaving all these discussions;", 
            "dur": "2.341", 
            "start": "586.534"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I remember when I was learning Chinese,", 
            "dur": "2.014", 
            "start": "588.875"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I would haggle\nand try to get two yen more,", 
            "dur": "3.06", 
            "start": "590.889"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to get that wonderful dumpling,\nand getting the discount;", 
            "dur": "3.53", 
            "start": "593.949"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or I would go to Roma", 
            "dur": "1.939", 
            "start": "597.479"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I&#39;d ask for directions\nto the best &quot;piazza.&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.469", 
            "start": "599.418"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was amazing.", 
            "dur": "1.3", 
            "start": "602.887"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The beautiful thing\nabout the shower conversation", 
            "dur": "2.286", 
            "start": "604.187"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is that it allows you to find wherever\nyou have a gap in your knowledge,", 
            "dur": "4.406", 
            "start": "606.473"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because you&#39;re having\na conversation on both ends.", 
            "dur": "3.22", 
            "start": "610.879"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "For example, it&#39;s easy to ask\nfor directions, how about receiving them?", 
            "dur": "4.143", 
            "start": "614.099"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Or even better, giving directions.", 
            "dur": "2.173", 
            "start": "618.242"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, the shower conversation forces you\nto have both side of the conversation.", 
            "dur": "4.095", 
            "start": "620.415"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And you don&#39;t need\nto have them in the shower.", 
            "dur": "2.694", 
            "start": "624.51"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Another wonderful thing\nis that you can have them anywhere.", 
            "dur": "2.901", 
            "start": "627.204"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You can have them in the shower,\nin your apartment,", 
            "dur": "2.396", 
            "start": "630.105"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "walking down in the streets,\nin the subway,", 
            "dur": "2.956", 
            "start": "632.501"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and seriously, if you&#39;re in the subway,", 
            "dur": "2.546", 
            "start": "635.457"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "speaking to yourself in a foreign\nlanguage in New York,", 
            "dur": "2.658", 
            "start": "638.003"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you&#39;ll fit right in.", 
            "dur": "1.361", 
            "start": "640.661"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You&#39;re fine.", 
            "dur": "1.637", 
            "start": "642.025"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s great,", 
            "dur": "1.254", 
            "start": "643.662"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because you don&#39;t depend on anything\nor anyone to get your practice,", 
            "dur": "4.314", 
            "start": "644.916"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I did this for years.", 
            "dur": "1.854", 
            "start": "649.23"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And later on I found\nthat professional athletes do, too.", 
            "dur": "2.925", 
            "start": "651.084"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Michael Phelps is known to visualize\nevery single one of his races,", 
            "dur": "4.284", 
            "start": "654.009"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "several times over,\nbefore jumping in water.", 
            "dur": "3.194", 
            "start": "658.293"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Worked great for him,", 
            "dur": "1.445", 
            "start": "661.487"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and it works great for me, too,", 
            "dur": "2.004", 
            "start": "662.932"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so it would work for you as well.", 
            "dur": "2.712", 
            "start": "664.936"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And now let&#39;s go to using the language.", 
            "dur": "3.313", 
            "start": "667.648"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because up to now, it&#39;s great,", 
            "dur": "1.72", 
            "start": "670.961"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we&#39;ve figured out\nhow to do all these things,", 
            "dur": "2.15", 
            "start": "672.681"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and that puts us in a really good position\nto use the language,", 
            "dur": "3.472", 
            "start": "674.831"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and for that I recommend\nyou find a conversation buddy.", 
            "dur": "4.174", 
            "start": "678.303"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "To find a conversation buddy,", 
            "dur": "2.124", 
            "start": "682.477"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I recommend you follow what I call\n&quot;The Buddy Formula.&quot;", 
            "dur": "4.894", 
            "start": "684.601"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that is a way that you can make sure", 
            "dur": "2.447", 
            "start": "689.495"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that your incentives are always aligned\nto use the new language.", 
            "dur": "5.286", 
            "start": "691.942"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So for that is,", 
            "dur": "1.365", 
            "start": "697.228"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the target language should be\nyour best language in common.", 
            "dur": "4.325", 
            "start": "698.593"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Why?", 
            "dur": "1.156", 
            "start": "702.918"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you&#39;re anything like me,", 
            "dur": "1.847", 
            "start": "704.074"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you like to learn languages,", 
            "dur": "1.86", 
            "start": "705.921"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so that you can communicate\nwith more people,", 
            "dur": "2.94", 
            "start": "707.781"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so that you can reach out", 
            "dur": "1.462", 
            "start": "710.721"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and understand a little bit more\nabout their brains and hearts.", 
            "dur": "3.915", 
            "start": "712.183"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And so, if we try to talk to\nsomeone in a foreign language", 
            "dur": "3.764", 
            "start": "716.098"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that both of us don&#39;t do really well,\nwhen we could be speaking English,", 
            "dur": "3.384", 
            "start": "719.862"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or whatever language you&#39;re\nmore comfortable with as a pair,", 
            "dur": "3.31", 
            "start": "723.246"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "odds are that you&#39;re going to revert\nto that language that is easier.", 
            "dur": "3.541", 
            "start": "726.556"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I recommend you to find someone\nwhere your best language in common", 
            "dur": "3.392", 
            "start": "730.097"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is your target language.", 
            "dur": "1.822", 
            "start": "733.489"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And if you can&#39;t find one locally,\ntry technology.", 
            "dur": "2.717", 
            "start": "735.311"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Or if you can travel,\nthat would be perfect.", 
            "dur": "3.447", 
            "start": "738.028"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There&#39;s a problem with that,\nand I realize it,", 
            "dur": "2.532", 
            "start": "741.475"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because it&#39;s difficult to find someone\nwho fits that profile exactly.", 
            "dur": "3.742", 
            "start": "744.007"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But I&#39;ve got good news.", 
            "dur": "1.724", 
            "start": "747.749"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I&#39;ve found that out when I was work,", 
            "dur": "2.844", 
            "start": "749.473"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and one of my colleagues,\nhe&#39;s a linguist, too,", 
            "dur": "2.38", 
            "start": "752.317"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "he speaks a ton of languages,", 
            "dur": "2.52", 
            "start": "754.697"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and our best language in common\nwas definitely English.", 
            "dur": "4.132", 
            "start": "757.217"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Our second best language in common:\ndefinitely French.", 
            "dur": "3.579", 
            "start": "761.349"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But we always spoke in German\nto each other in the office.", 
            "dur": "5.019", 
            "start": "764.928"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Why was that?", 
            "dur": "1.779", 
            "start": "769.947"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was because there were people\nin the office who spoke English;", 
            "dur": "3.204", 
            "start": "771.726"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "there were people in the office\nwho spoke French.", 
            "dur": "2.524", 
            "start": "774.93"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But we could talk about Friday\nand Saturday night in German,", 
            "dur": "3.425", 
            "start": "777.454"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and nobody had any idea\nwhat we were talking about.", 
            "dur": "3.072", 
            "start": "780.879"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So it can also be your best\nsecret language in common.", 
            "dur": "3.694", 
            "start": "783.957"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "1.667", 
            "start": "787.651"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it becomes such a convenient tool.", 
            "dur": "2.183", 
            "start": "789.318"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You can have it with your friends", 
            "dur": "1.956", 
            "start": "791.501"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and you get the sense of privacy\nin public.", 
            "dur": "2.936", 
            "start": "793.457"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "No matter where you are,\nyou can have a private conversation.", 
            "dur": "3.066", 
            "start": "796.393"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, let&#39;s recap.", 
            "dur": "1.685", 
            "start": "799.459"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "With the first technique", 
            "dur": "1.507", 
            "start": "801.144"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we allow ourselves to break\nthrough the barrier of language", 
            "dur": "3.637", 
            "start": "802.651"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and to explore the uncharted territory", 
            "dur": "2.928", 
            "start": "806.288"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of sounds and structures\noutside our database.", 
            "dur": "2.724", 
            "start": "809.216"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Then with the second one,", 
            "dur": "1.855", 
            "start": "811.94"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we learn how to take notes", 
            "dur": "1.826", 
            "start": "813.795"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and how to make sure\nthat we can take notes", 
            "dur": "2.106", 
            "start": "815.621"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in a way that we can replicate\nthose sounds and structures later.", 
            "dur": "3.288", 
            "start": "817.727"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Then we can check the mistakes\nby finding a stickler.", 
            "dur": "3.89", 
            "start": "821.015"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Fourth: Practice.", 
            "dur": "1.429", 
            "start": "824.905"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Have shower conversations,\nwherever you want to be.", 
            "dur": "2.929", 
            "start": "826.334"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then, follow the Buddy Formula,", 
            "dur": "2.241", 
            "start": "829.263"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and you can find somebody\nto practice your language with.", 
            "dur": "3.18", 
            "start": "831.504"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And after that,", 
            "dur": "2.082", 
            "start": "834.684"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Italian) we get to\na truly beautiful place,", 
            "dur": "3.766", 
            "start": "836.766"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(German) where learning languages", 
            "dur": "2.03", 
            "start": "840.532"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is no longer something stressful,\ndifficult and boring,", 
            "dur": "4.08", 
            "start": "842.562"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Spanish) but rather\na world of possibilities.", 
            "dur": "3.158", 
            "start": "846.642"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A world, where each of us\nhas the opportunity to explore", 
            "dur": "2.708", 
            "start": "849.8"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(French) new cultures and\nall the different ways of living.", 
            "dur": "4.818", 
            "start": "852.508"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Br. Portuguese)\nThe greatest reward from this,", 
            "dur": "2.479", 
            "start": "857.326"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is that we end up learning\nmore about ourselves.", 
            "dur": "3.249", 
            "start": "859.805"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Greek) As of now,\nit may all sound Greek for you.", 
            "dur": "3.956", 
            "start": "863.054"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But that doesn&#39;t mean\nthat you can&#39;t learn it.", 
            "dur": "4.666", 
            "start": "867.01"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Mandarin Chinese)\n&quot;A journey of a thousand miles", 
            "dur": "2.329", 
            "start": "872.185"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "begins with the first step.&quot;", 
            "dur": "1.418", 
            "start": "874.514"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(English) And this is not a problem,\nbecause now you know how to walk.", 
            "dur": "4.994", 
            "start": "875.932"
        }, 
